topItems.headline: What a Lego x Nike SB collab looks like
topItems.description: BespokeIND is gearing up to release a new custom creation, presenting the colorful Nike SB Dunk Low LEGO, which plays on the childhood obsession with LEGOs.

topItems.headline: How lockdown unleashed a thriving online market for colorfoul clothes
topItems.description: Multicoloured striped tank tops, pink scalloped dungarees, rainbow wrist warmers… If bright and bold colour is what you’re looking for, Marielle Wyse is your woman and Wyse London your brand.

topItems.headline: Hermès store opens in Harbour City, Hong Kong
topItems.description: Hermès has unveiled its new store at the Harbour City shopping centre, double the size of its previous boutique there.

otherItems.headline: Great outfits in fashion history: Taylor Swift in a pearl-encrusted romper
otherItems.description: There are perfectly good celebrity style moments, and then there are the looks that really stick with you, the ones you try desperately to recreate at home. In 'Great Outfits in Fashion History,' Fashionista editors are revisiting their all-time favorite looks.

otherItems.headline: Meet the Green Lady of Brooklyn and her evergreen approach to life
otherItems.description: For the past 20 years or so, Elizabeth Sweetheart, 74, has dressed head to toe in a bright lime green, with hair dyed to match.

topItems.headline: Gucci is selling upside-down glasses for £470 and people are confused
topItems.description: Gucci is known for setting trends – but we’re not sure this is one that will catch on.

topItems.headline: Gucci footwear discounted up to 20 percent off for DSW sale
topItems.description: Whether you’re looking for some personal wardrobe staples or shopping for a great gift for your favorite fashion lover, you’re sure to find something perfect.

topItems.headline: Gucci's $1,100 USD Apple AirPods Pro Case Doubles as a Trunk Necklace
topItems.description: The Italian imprint also released a $460 USD GG Marmont AirPods pouch.

otherItems.headline: Gucci releases non-binary gift guide featuring new MX collection
otherItems.description: In a welcome shift towards more gender-inclusive representation in the fashion industry, and a historic first for the designer brand, Gucci has introduced a “for them” section to their annual gift guide which draws from their entirely non-binary collection of clothing and apparel.

otherItems.headline: Gucci releases details on the 2021 Ready-To-Wear Spring Collection
otherItems.description: Here's a sneak peek of the upcoming Spring 2021 Ready-To-Wear collection from Gucci.

topItems.headline: Zara to shutter Grand Rue Store, Luxembourg
topItems.description: Following a dispute over the cost of rent in the Grand Rue, Spanish ready-to-wear brand Zara will focus its retail strategy in Luxembourg on its three shopping mall outlets.

otherItems.headline: Zara’s New Collection Is Made Of Vintage Pieces, Designed By 4 Rising Designers
otherItems.description: On Thursday, Spanish fashion brand Zara announced a partnership with the Council of Fashion Designers in America (CFDA).
